run(sql="
with cte as(
select date, sessionId, pogId from(
    select distinct to_date(FROM_UNIXTIME((ss.startTime) / 1000)) as date, 
                    pv.sessionId,
                    pv.pogId,
                    ss.utmContent,
                    row_number() over(partition by pv.sessionId order by ss.startTime) as rank
    from `last3Days(sessionSummary)` ss left join `last3Days(productView)` pv 
    on ss.sessionId=pv.sessionId 
    order by date)
where lower(utmContent) like '%cpt%' and rank=1)

select distinct a.date, 
                count(distinct case when b.NM3SO<=25 and NM3SO>10 then a.sessionId end) as LTE10 
from cte a left join `temp.nmso_bau` b 
on a.pogId=b.pogId 
group by a.date
order by a.date desc
",1000)
